high_descs: Turn left and move towards the door then turn left move towards the refrigerator then turn left and face the table.
Pick up the head of lettuce on top of the sponge from the table.
Turn right and move towards the wall then turn left and face the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the lettuce on the plate on the top shelf, close the refrigerator, wait, open the refrigerator, pick up the lettuce from the top shelf and close the refrigerator door.
Turn left and move towards the kitchen counter then turn right and face the table.
Place the lettuce on the table between the sponge and the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce on the table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk forwards, turn left, walk forwards, turn to face the white table on your left.
Pick up the lettuce that is sitting on the table.
Turn right and move forwards towards the wall, then turn right and face the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator and place the lettuce inside, close the door, then open it again, and take the lettuce back out
Close the refrigerator, turn left and walk forwards, turn right to face a white table
Place the lettuce on the table
anns.task_desc: Chill a lettuce before replacing it on the table

high_descs: Turn around to face the far wall and go to the white table which is now on your left.
Pick up the head of lettuce that is on the white table.
Go to the refrigerator to the right of the table.
Open the refrigerator door and put the lettuce on the blue plate on the top rack and close the refrigerator door.
Open the refrigerator door and pick up the lettuce on the blue plate on the top rack.
Go the white table to the left of the refrigerator and place the lettuce between the sponge and the knife.
anns.task_desc: Refrigerate the head of lettuce on the white table for meal preparation.
